sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelStorage: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving Request
        participant Client as External Client
        participant Gateway as Istio Gateway /<br/>OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        participant VS as VirtualService /<br/>HTTPRoute<br/>80/TCP mTLS (Istio)
        participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy /<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant ModelStorage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/HF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Gateway->>VS: Forward request<br/>mTLS (Istio mesh)
        VS->>OAuthProxy: Route to predictor service<br/>mTLS (Istio)
        OAuthProxy->>Predictor: Authenticated request<br/>HTTP localhost
        Note over Predictor,ModelStorage: Init: storage-initializer downloads model
        Predictor-->>OAuthProxy: Prediction response
        OAuthProxy-->>VS: Response
        VS-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result<br/>HTTPS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,DecodePod: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService (Disaggregated Prefill/Decode)
        participant LLMGateway as Gateway<br/>(HTTPRoute)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        participant Scheduler as InferencePool<br/>Scheduler<br/>gRPC TLS
        participant PrefillPod as Prefill Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS<br/>Self-signed TLS
        participant DecodePod as Decode Pod<br/>(via routing sidecar)<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS

        Client->>LLMGateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        LLMGateway->>Scheduler: Route to InferencePool<br/>gRPC TLS
        Scheduler->>PrefillPod: Prefill request<br/>HTTPS (self-signed certs)
        PrefillPod->>DecodePod: KV cache transfer<br/>(routing sidecar)<br/>HTTPS (self-signed certs)
        DecodePod-->>Scheduler: Token generation response
        Scheduler-->>LLMGateway: Streaming response
        LLMGateway-->>Client: SSE / JSON response<br/>HTTPS
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over LMCache,NodePV: Flow 3: LocalModel Cache Download
        participant LMCache as LocalModelCache CR
        participant LMCtrl as localmodel-controller
        participant LMAgent as localmodelnode-agent
        participant DLJob as Download Job<br/>(storage-initializer)
        participant CloudStore as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        participant NodePV as Node Local PV

        LMCache->>LMCtrl: CRD Watch event
        LMCtrl->>LMCtrl: Create PV/PVC<br/>K8s API HTTPS
        LMCtrl->>LMAgent: Update LocalModelNode spec<br/>K8s API HTTPS
        LMAgent->>DLJob: Create download Job<br/>K8s API HTTPS
        DLJob->>CloudStore: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
        CloudStore-->>DLJob: Model artifacts
        DLJob->>NodePV: Write to local filesystem
        DLJob-->>LMAgent: Job completion status
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,ISvcB: Flow 4: InferenceGraph DAG Routing
        participant IGRouter as kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
        participant TokenReview as K8s TokenReview API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
        participant ISvcA as InferenceService A<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        participant ISvcB as InferenceService B<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS

        Client->>IGRouter: POST /<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS (optional)
        IGRouter->>TokenReview: Validate bearer token<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        TokenReview-->>IGRouter: Token valid
        IGRouter->>ISvcA: Fan-out: Step 1<br/>HTTP mTLS (mesh)
        ISvcA-->>IGRouter: Partial result
        IGRouter->>ISvcB: Fan-out: Step 2<br/>(ensemble/sequence/splitter)<br/>HTTP mTLS (mesh)
        ISvcB-->>IGRouter: Final result
        IGRouter-->>Client: Aggregated response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    end
